data.description: This beautiful 6 bedroom 3.5 bath home in the heart of Pembroke is waiting for you! This home was recently remodeled with a completely finished basement. The kitchen has custom cabinets, granite countertops, walk in pantry and so much more.  The main level has lovely hardwood flooring, the large family room leads to a covered porch and amazing views!  You will find newer carpet on the upper level with 3 large secondary bedrooms and large bathroom.  The primary suite has a bonus room with endless possibilities and a large bathroom with soaking tub and walk in shower.  You will find a laundry room on the upper level near the bedrooms and a new laundry room in the finished basement.  The walk out basement has 2 full bedrooms and 1 bathroom, you will find an incredible family room to spread out! Castle Rock Golf course and Treasure Island park are within walking distance. Only 20 minutes to VA Tech and Blacksburg.  This great property will not last long call for a showing today!
